
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README: Modules-Templates
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This directory contains pre-made templates to create application's module

Upon creating a module, the template files will be copied to the new Module.


== Architecture

- Templates must reside in their own directory with the proper

- Requirement: Each template must have the following file

    /Modules-Templates/
            |
            |_ /Views
                    |
                    |_ /_layout
                            |
                            |_ /container.html


                     
- Additionally you can add any files in your Views
You must know that directory starting with _ (underscore)
                    
    /Modules-Templates/
            |
            |_ /Views
                    |
                    |_ /_layout
                            |
                            |_ /container.html
                    |
                    |_ /_assets
                            |
                            |_ /css
                            |
                            |_ /js
                            |
                            |_ /images




- Adding Controllers in the templates

    /Modules-Templates/
            |
            |_ /Views
                    |
                    |_ /_layout
                            |
                            |_ /container.html
                    |
                    |_ /_assets
                            |
                            |_ /css
                            |
                            |_ /js
                            |
                            |_ /images
                    |
                    |_ /Index
                            |
                            |_ /index.html
                            |
                            |_ /login.html
                            |
                            |_ /logout.html
            |
            |_ /Controllers
                    |
                    |_ /Index.php


